---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ghana Sector Deep Dives: Agriculture, Fintech, Real Estate, Healthcare"
  description="Ghana-specific sector intelligence. Not generic emerging market frameworks. Deep dives into agriculture, fintech, real estate, healthcare, logistics, and more."
  keywords="Ghana sectors, Ghana agriculture, Ghana fintech, Ghana real estate, Ghana healthcare, Ghana logistics, sector analysis Ghana"
>
  <div class="hero" style="padding-top:7rem;">
    <div class="hero-noise"></div>
    <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;">
      <span class="hero-tag">Sector Intelligence</span>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,2.8rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:0.75rem;letter-spacing:-1px;">Sector <span class="gradient-text">Deep Dives</span></h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;">Ghana-specific sector intelligence. Not generic emerging market frameworks. Each sector analysis includes market sizing, competitive dynamics, infrastructure requirements, and honest risk assessment.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
      <p>Sector deep dives are being rebuilt with fresh Cycle 001+ data through the v3.0 publishing pipeline. Each article passes 8 stages with 3 mandatory quality gates.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card coming-soon reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="feature-card__icon">&#x1F33E;</div>
        <h3>Agriculture: Beyond Cocoa</h3>
        <p>Cassava, shea, palm oil, poultry: where the real margins are. Updated with Hormuz fuel cost impact on agro-processing economics.</p>
        <div class="card-meta"><span class="pipeline-badge">In Pipeline</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card coming-soon reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="feature-card__icon">&#x1F4F1;</div>
        <h3>Fintech Landscape 2026</h3>
        <p>Mobile money, digital lending, remittance corridors. Updated with BoG rate cut impact and diaspora legislation cluster.</p>
        <div class="card-meta"><span class="pipeline-badge">In Pipeline</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card coming-soon reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="feature-card__icon">&#x1F3E0;</div>
        <h3>Real Estate: The Diaspora Trap</h3>
        <p>Why most diaspora real estate investments underperform. Land title risks, construction fraud, and what actually works.</p>
        <div class="card-meta"><span class="pipeline-badge">In Pipeline</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
